- [redoc](https://image-steganography-d3fau1t.herokuapp.com/redoc)

## Appendix

### Check setting file

You can check the image path or other required values.

```json
{
  "encoding": "utf8",
  "bits": 8,
  "token_string": "#secret#",
  "message": "./message.txt",
  "in_image": "./image.png",
  "out_image": "./output.png",
  "modified_image": "./output.png"
}
```

